'''José María Canale Domínguez''' (born 20 July 1996) is a Paraguayan professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[centre-back]] for [[Argentine Primera División]] side [[Club Atlético Lanús|Lanús]] and the [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay national team]].

==Career==
Canale debuted for [[Club Libertad|Libertad]] on 28 May 2015 in a 3–0 win against [[Club Sportivo San Lorenzo|San Lorenzo]] in the [[Paraguayan Primera División]].

On 29 July 2021, he moved to Argentina to join [[Newell's Old Boys]] on loan.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2021-10-25 |title=Acuerdo para la contratación de José Canale - Noticias CANOB |url=https://www.newellsoldboys.com.ar/noticias/primera-division/2021/07/29/Acuerdo-para-la-contratacion-de-Jose-Canale |access-date=2024-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211025203248/https://www.newellsoldboys.com.ar/noticias/primera-division/2021/07/29/Acuerdo-para-la-contratacion-de-Jose-Canale |archive-date=25 October 2021 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=José Maria Canale sería cedido a Newell's de Argentina - Libertad - ABC Color |url=https://www.abc.com.py/deportes/futbol/libertad/2021/07/29/jose-maria-canale-seria-cedido-a-newells-de-argentina/ |access-date=2024-08-19 |website=www.abc.com.py |language=es}}</ref>

On 7 December 2022, he left Libertad permanently to join [[Club Atlético Lanús|Lanús]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-12-07 |title=José Canale refuerza a Lanús |url=https://d10.ultimahora.com/jose-canale-refuerza-lanus-n3037614 |access-date=2024-08-19 |website=D10 |language=es}}</ref> In August 2024, he joined [[Liga MX]] side [[Querétaro F.C.|Querétaro]] on loan, with an option to buy.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Liga MX: José Canale es nuevo jugador del Querétaro |url=https://www.tusbuenasnoticias.com/noticias/deportes/2024/08/16/36438-liga-mx-jose-canale-refuerza-al-queretaro |access-date=2024-08-19 |website=TusBuenasNoticias |language=es}}</ref>

